    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and delivered through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained for precision, featuring reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry. This example exhibits the expected cosmetic patina of a well-loved driver, but its performance envelope remains uncompromised, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline and exceptional lateral grip.",
      "price": 32500.0,
